        description:
            "📍 Location: Valencia\n\n📅 Full-time | Start date: Immediate\n\nAbout YOUNG\n\nYOUNG is a fast-growing group of companies focused on disruption and innovation across various sectors. We build, invest, and scale businesses driven by a strong entrepreneurial spirit. Within YOUNG, our YOUNG Non Core department focuses, among other things, on small and unique hospitality concepts in our home base Valencia as well as in the Netherlands. Our ambition is to bundle and grow a strong hospitality portfolio. In most concepts, we partner with co-entrepreneurs who manage daily operations, while we invest and support in strategy, branding, and expansion.\n\nCurrently, our hospitality group is expanding rapidly, and we’re looking for a junior hospitality talent who wants to help us grow. \n\nYour role\n\nAs a Junior Hospitality Manager, you'll be supporting and developing hospitality concepts primarily in Valencia, while also providing remote assistance to our hospitality locations in the Netherlands. You'll assist in daily operations, branding, and strategic growth of our international hospitality portfolio. This is a unique opportunity to grow within an entrepreneurial environment and build your hospitality career.\n\nWhat you’ll do\n\n✅ Support and help grow our hospitality portfolio in Valencia, and provide remote operational and strategic support to our locations in the Netherlands.\n\n✅ Help monitor operational and financial performance of our hospitality businesses and ensure the right entrepreneurs are positioned for success.\n\n✅ Assist in developing the overall branding, Instagram page, and website for YOUNG Hospitality.\n\n✅ Help identify new hospitality opportunities in Valencia, the Netherlands, and beyond.\n\n✅ Collaborate closely with co-entrepreneurs, ensuring smooth operations at all locations.\n\n✅ Support in recruitment and team-building as the group expands.\n\n✅ Assist with reporting and performance analysis of hospitality businesses.\n\nWhat we’re looking for\n\n💡 An entrepreneurial mindset—someone who treats YOUNG’s hospitality division as their own.\n\n🎯 Some experience or strong interest in hospitality, ideally in an entrepreneurial environment.\n\n📈 Strong organizational and communication skills, eager to learn and grow both strategically and operationally.\n\n🤝 A natural networker—someone comfortable building relationships with entrepreneurs, suppliers, and partners.\n\n📲 Familiarity with branding and social media, excited to build and improve our online presence.\n\n🏆 Hands-on, results-oriented, and motivated to help grow our hospitality division.\n\nWhat we offer\n\n🚀 The opportunity to build your career within YOUNG’s hospitality division.\n\n💰 Competitive junior-level salary between €18,000 and €27,000 annually, based on experience and skills.\n\n🌍 A dynamic environment and network within YOUNG to accelerate your growth.\n\n🏡 Based in Valencia, in a vibrant and entrepreneurial atmosphere, with exposure to international operations.\n\n📲 Freedom to develop and execute branding, social media, and growth initiatives.\n\nApply\n\nAre you ready to join YOUNG Hospitality and build your career in a fast-growing entrepreneurial company? Apply immediately by sending an email to wim@young.com or apply via LinkedIn.",
